reviews.content: Marggie Leturno, PA - is the best of the Best and Langley is surely lucky to have an EXCEPTIONAL practitioner like her. The whole team in Citrus county is TOP notch!

I have had nothing but good visits here. I see Dr. Welty and I love her. She's very down to earth , caring and is a great listener. She didn't talk over me, or make me feel uncomfortable at all. Also did not make me feel as if she didn't believe me. I would definitely recommend this facility

I would not send my worse enemy to this place. they told my wife she had stage IV breast cancer when all along it was just a benign tumor. they have no idea what they are doing. for your own safety, do not go here.
